snippet.title: Microsoft - Deadly Tide Theatrical Trailer
snippet.description:
Microsoft rail pano shooter. Visual concept and animation by Tony Stutterheim. Music composition and sound effects by Mark Stratford.
Trailer that appeared in theaters around the world.
